snippet.title: Harmony Trailer   -  (promotional video for the game)
snippet.description:
Video trailer for the computer game Harmony.

This video was made in August 2011. The game was released in November 2009.
To get the game for free or see more of Rabotiks art go to:
www.rabotik.nl
